  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effects of a mindfulness-based meditation
      intervention on quality of life, sleep and mood in adolescents with cancer compared to a
      control group.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
